Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:14.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure is peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:18.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:26.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This calmness is going to spoil us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:32.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife's been sleeping all day recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:35.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She hardly even makes breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:39.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,"How suddenly the morning comes in Spring", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:39.38,notes,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)}Dawn in Spring by Meng Hao-ran
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:43.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's gotten really forgetful these days too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:47.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other time she left our kid at the market.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:48.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:53.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hope she hasn't forgotten who\Nyou are when you get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:57.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I actually wish she would.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:04.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your wife doesn't have trouble\Nsleeping at night, does she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:08.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She sleeps with a loud snore all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:09.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:11.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:14.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It gives {\i1}me{\i0} a hard time whenever I try to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:16.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have snoring medication if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:23.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:29.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what you were just talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:33.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,About the snoring medication?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:36.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, about forgetting things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:42.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it bad if you can't sleep at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:45.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there something that's bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:49.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:55.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:57.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help me, Kaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a weird thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:00.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weird thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:06.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A crab?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten crabs too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:12.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They always come from the river\Naround this time of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:15.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:20.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're Kaji's friend, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he's not. I just met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:25.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a Mushi-shi, Ginko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:27.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mushi-shi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mind if I step in for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:33.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:36.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Kaji's mother, Sayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:41.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how she always is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:44.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's always been on the slow side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:47.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean, she's been forgetting things a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:52.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But ever since sometime last spring,\Nshe'd forget really weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:56.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a big crowd of people buying dango that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I got some for Mom on my way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:02.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:05.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never had anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:10.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? You've\Nhad them every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:12.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that I'm eating behind your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:21.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom had forgotten everything about dango.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:24.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And another time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:27.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured I should sell off the ones I don't wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:30.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:34.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't remember having this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You took really good care of it because\Nyou said it was really expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:38.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:47.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't worn it much because\Nit doesn't look good on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:53.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'd just forgotten the patterned kimonos\Nthat she doesn't wear often.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:56.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's cold today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:57.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be so strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:07.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:10.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,All I did was sneeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:12.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sneeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:16.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'd forgotten what a sneeze was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:19.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we went to a relatives' place for New Year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:24.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaji, who were those two people in the back again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:27.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Masa and Aunt Mitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And beside them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:34.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even her sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That does sound strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:42.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sounds more like progressive\Namnesia than forgetfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:43.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:49.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she's always awake working, day and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:54.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She used to take naps under that tree between chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:59.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's definitely something wrong with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dinner's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:06.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please join us, Ginko-san. Though\Nwe don't have anything fancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:07.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:14.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Write down as much stuff that your\Nmom's forgotten as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:25.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:29.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a kagezen for my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:31.68,notes,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)}Kagezen: meal offering
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:31.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kagezen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:36.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. He's a traveling salesman, traveling for a full year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:41.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, they say he won't be\Nhungry on his trip this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:44.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just to make me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:48.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She hadn't forgotten that he's\Ndied or something, has she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:50.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Time to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:53.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a waste of food, I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not all that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:58.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you're eating that much less, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:02.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who do you think Dad's traveling for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:06.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must be a lot hungrier than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:10.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though he hardly makes any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:13.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could just work nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:16.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He should be home by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He hasn't even sent a single letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:24.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because he makes you worry so much
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:27.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,that you end up going dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:27.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:31.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How rude of him to just eat and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:39.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:43.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he just wants his father to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:49.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband's got nothing going for\Nhim other than being a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:53.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must have gotten lost somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:58.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like he's not just worried about his dad though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:01.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:06.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must have been called here by him, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:11.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I got the gist of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:14.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you can tell me about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:18.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:21.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:25.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, for my son, and of course for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:28.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:36.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm eventually going to forget\Nabout him and my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:41.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then I'm going to forget that I've forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:48.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just so afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:52.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, for the most part.
